{{refimprove|date=December 2010}} {{Infobox Magazine| title = Studia theologica| frequency = Quarterly| category = [[Theology]], [[Philosophy]], [[Church history|Church History]]| publisher = Palacký University of Olomouc| firstdate = 1999| country = {{flag|Czech Republic}}| language = [[Czech language|Czech]], [[Slovak language|Slovak]]| website = [http://www.studiatheologica.eu Studia theologica]| issn = 1212-8570 }}
'''''Studia theologica''''' ({{ISSN|1212-8570}}, in [[Czech language|Czech]] and [[Slovak language|Slovak]] languages with English abstracts) is a [[peer review|peer-reviewed]] quarterly [[academic journal]] of [[theology]], [[philosophy]] and [[church history]]. Since 1999, it is issued in co-operation of four Czech and Slovak theological colleges: [[Palacký University of Olomouc#Saints Cyril and Methodius Faculty of Theology|St. Cyril and Methodius Faculty of Theology]] of Palacký University in Olomouc, [http://www.tf.jcu.cz Faculty of Theology] of [[University of South Bohemia in České Budějovice]], Catholic Theological Faculty of [[Charles University in Prague]] and Theological Faculty of [[University of Trnava]] in Bratislava.<ref>Dominik Opatrný, "10. výročí časopisu Studia theologica," ''Teologické texty'' 20, nr. 3 (2009): 156. ([http://www.teologicketexty.cz/casopis/2009-3/10-vyroci-casopisu-Studia-theologica.html online]).</ref>
